# Personal Standup Style

Personal style overlay for the `ug-standup` plugin.
Loaded by `standup-format` and `standup-aggregate` at runtime.
Edit freely — changes take effect on the next standup run.
Lines starting with `#` and commented-out sections are guidance; remove or replace them.

